        			<p>I'm aerobatic pilot in the category UNLIMITED, a member of the Czech national team in aerobatics and professional airshow pilot. </p>
        			<p>Birth: Feb 23, 1972 in Melnik.</p>
        			<p>Total hours flown: 700, of which 500 aerobatic (4/2014). </p>
        			<p>My motto: <em>Whatever I do I do it to the fullest. I either get up there or I don`t.</em></p>
