                <p class="text-justify"><b>Favourite airplane: </b>Z 37 Cmelak (bumblebee) – shape and sounds catches my heart and preferably I`d love to buy it for my dad for “tramping”. Then of course all World War II aircraft, and then our racers – only they are more from composite, otherwise it`s almost the same</p>
